race.comment: TWO GIRLS (1) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 1.75 lengths (29.92) at Launceston. Looks well placed and can measure up again. TIMES FLYING (5) recorded a 1.5 lengths win (25.83) in a Other last time at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. FISHERMAN'S WISH (4) scored by 4 lengths last time (16.01) in a Grade 5 over 278m at Launceston. Has four wins already from this draw. Something for the Multiples: SEATON (6)
